channel.title: TheDrunkBunny's Sketchbook
channel.description:
So instead of spamming the graphic's forum with shit I draw, I'mma do what Frell did and make a sketchbook.
ANYWAY, let's start this off shall we? :)
[img]http://img441.imageshack.us/img441/1070/littleredridinghood.png[/img] Who's afraid of the big, bad wolf? ^_^
LOLSHITHAVEN'TUPDATEDINFOREVER.
[img]http://fc02.deviantart.net/fs71/f/2012/078/4/b/eyes_upon_the_moon_by_kasuralixa-d4tc65k.jpg[/img]
[img]http://th06.deviantart.net/fs70/PRE/f/2012/070/a/1/so_i_drew_a_khajiit___by_kasuralixa-d4seela.png[/img] Supposed to be a Khajiit.. kind of just looks like a cat.. but.. whatever.
[img]http://fc08.deviantart.net/fs70/f/2012/103/7/4/dark_elf____because_i_can__by_kasuralixa-d4w3hs3.jpg[/img] Dark Elf.. From The Elder Scrolls.. again.. I drew an Orc too but dear god it looked like a mutilated pig.
[img]http://fc04.deviantart.net/fs71/f/2012/103/7/4/werewolf_digital_sketch_thang__by_kasuralixa-d4w3htd.jpg[/img] Werewolf sketch. Just a redone/touched up version of a RL sketch I did a looong time ago.
